cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper deals with Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and their interpretation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a multi-channel attention mechanism for feature space analysis, which is related to attention models in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper applies the proposed method to multi-attribute recognition, which is a common task in multimedia (cs.MM).
